Ask HN: Has Anyone Used Flareact?
text:
Moving SSR to the edge (Cloudflare) while benefiting from hybrid rendering options and a DX like Next.js sounds like a great option for new projects.

Plus, they seem to support React Native.

Anyone out here who built something in production using Flareact? My personal concern is that it ends up in lock-in on Cloudflare.
